    UNBLOCKED -->|I'm done for now| EXIT["Exit — resume when data arrives"]
    UNBLOCKED -->|I'm blocked| AGENT["See: Agent Run<br/>(debug mode)"]
    UNBLOCKED -->|take me to the docs| DOCS["Open docs in browser"] --> UNBLOCKED